primary_question: Is there statistical evidence of vintage-related artifacts in the ND international migration time series?

level_shift_2009_2010.interpretation: Significant mean increase at first vintage transition

level_shift_2019_2020.caveat: Cannot separate vintage effect from COVID effect

placebo_comparison.note: Compare F-statistics at transitions vs non-transition years

power_limitations.note: Very small samples severely limit statistical power. Failure to reject null does not imply no effect.

overall_assessment.recommendation: Proceed with caution; consider sensitivity analyses
key_uncertainties: Cannot distinguish methodology change from real demographic shifts
Power too low to detect moderate effects
